{"tid":1999034,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓成日呼吸好急","createTime":"2020-05-03T01:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T18:31:19.000Z","uid":30484,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4c268121bd540a82c26d6c9403997d0671c88f","tid":1999034,"uid":30484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"5個月英短。唔知係咪熱，隻貓呢兩日開始全天候訓教模式。有人無人都keep住眼訓，不過食得又柯得，我又驚郁得少，諗住同佢玩一分鐘左右佢都喘氣咁。個心跳得勁快。望住佢個肚郁動得好勁。仲有一兩下用口呼吸，見到咁樣唔敢同佢玩太耐。關唔關心臟事呀。之前無咁既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zptQfx3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzptQfx3.png&h=a8335097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1a8d23aa8876d87cc09d6515b9eb9bf6254e05e","tid":1999034,"uid":324330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"隻手好想..........<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189a80d7c204503ff0a2453a339fe925e2fa4094","tid":1999034,"uid":80042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"喘氣有機會關心臟事呀<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主主人及早就醫"},{"pid":"97b3b4acc98b7eaf53c4c516a093aa2fb894c8f9","tid":1999034,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189a80d7c204503ff0a2453a339fe925e2fa4094","tid":1999034,"uid":80042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"喘氣有機會關心臟事呀<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主主人及早就醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a950b0e85c68b27ba7bff51c1c8cabb048c38063","tid":1999034,"uid":12566